document_notes.text:
This update for python3 fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2023-6597: Fixed symlink bug in cleanup of tempfile.TemporaryDirectory (bsc#1219666).
- CVE-2022-48566: Make compare_digest more constant-time (bsc#1214691).

notes.text: An issue was discovered in compare_digest in Lib/hmac.py in Python through 3.9.1. Constant-time-defeating optimisations were possible in the accumulator variable in hmac.compare_digest.
